title: Holmes  Right - Seed
description:
In Holmes Makes it Right, Mike will be taking on disasters that would make other contractors run. The kinds of circumstances where you don't just need a contractor, you need a miracle.

All episodes are full-length. Every video is at least TV/VHS quality. BIG THANKS to all the original uploaders.
